# ESLint and Prettier Setup

This project uses ESLint with the Next.js recommended configuration (`next/core-web-vitals`) and integrates Prettier for code formatting. The ESLint config extends both `next/core-web-vitals` and `prettier` to avoid conflicts between linting and formatting rules. Prettier settings are defined in [.prettierrc](mdc:.prettierrc).

- Use `pnpm lint` to run ESLint.
- Use `pnpm format` to format code with Prettier.
- Prettier ignores files and folders listed in [.prettierignore](mdc:.prettierignore).
